      <akn:section eId="sec_32_1231_11">
        <akn:num>32-1231.11</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Penalties.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-1231_11_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>An employer who willfully violates ยง 32-1231.03 shall be subject to a civil penalty of $ 1,000 for the 1st offense, $ 1,500 for the 2nd offense, and $ 2,000 for the 3rd and each subsequent offense.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_32-1231_11_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>An employer who fails to post the notice of rights as required by ยง 32-1231.04(a) shall be assessed a civil penalty not to exceed $ 50 for each day that the employer fails to post the notice; provided, that the total penalty shall not exceed $ 250, unless the ongoing violation is willful.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
